maybe even a reasonable bathroom singer? These are all his identities too. =
But why don't we refer to them when we speak of Tendulkar? Because his cent=
ral defining identity for us is his cricket.</SPAN></DIV>
<DIV><SPAN></SPAN=
> </DIV>
<DIV><SPAN>Same way, each deity eventually is everything. But=
