ole new world! She banishes the very roots of the sense of strife and uglin=
ess from your system... the knowledge that She exists is enough to incapaci=
tate you from asking anything
 more. She is THE greatest poetry of all=
 possible Universes of all possible cycles of creation.</SPAN></DIV>
